data.title: Which Devilman Crybaby character are you?
data.text:
Evil, phlegmatic, and mysterious. You are very logical, even if it means going to the extremes. You do not believe in love, but are willing to protect your friends till the very end. You have many, many secrets within you (prob being the devil) and will make sure your identity is secure.

You have a heart of gold, you sensitive and caring demon. Even if your friends are quite devilish, you still respect and care about them deeply. Your actions are often guided by emotions, and you often see good even in the most evil of creatures.

You see more than what is just on the surface. Similar to Akira, you would do anything in order to help others in need. Although some people may see you as clueless, you are aware of many things around you, especially emotions.

You're a bit of a jealous b, but you're actually quite kind hearted and respectful! Once you're determined, it's hard to get you down! Sometimes, you're a little arrogant and sexually thirsty, but hey it's not that harmful right? ;)
